name: BTV Frequencies 002 - Orantes Mantis
description: Beyond the Void series by RocketSpaceboy. The BTV Frequencies work examines the frequencies received in the interdimensional existence beyond space and time. This specific piece is part of the Frequencies Collection. Orantes Mantis inhabits a realm caught in an endless cycle of chaos and sanity. The only purpose for existence in this realm is to consume. The most valuable item in this realm is flesh. Love, Life, and Death are all the same to the Orantes Mantis.
